257
00:32:44.550 --> 00:32:46.840
G
-Gohan-san!

258
00:32:49.210 --> 00:32:50.840
Irmãozão!

259
00:32:52.590 --> 00:32:54.210
Irmãozão!

260
00:32:54.210 --> 00:32:56.800
Ei, Goten!

261
00:32:59.090 --> 00:33:02.590
